objects.name: izlet
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE izlet (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, datum DATE, plezalisce INTEGER REFERENCES plezalisce (id), ime TEXT)

objects.name: je_splezal
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE je_splezal (nacin TEXT, datum_preplezane_smeri DATE, otrok INTEGER REFERENCES otrok (id), smer INTEGER REFERENCES smer (id), PRIMARY KEY (otrok, smer))

objects.name: otrok
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE otrok (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, ime TEXT, priimek TEXT, datum_rojstva DATE, leto_vpisa DATE)

objects.name: plezalisce
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE plezalisce (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, ime TEXT)

objects.name: pripada
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE pripada (otrok INTEGER REFERENCES otrok (id), skupina INTEGER REFERENCES skupina (id))

objects.name: racun
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE racun (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY NOT NULL, otrok INTEGER REFERENCES otrok (id), datum DATE NOT NULL, placano BOOLEAN, znesek DECIMAL, UNIQUE (otrok, datum))

objects.name: skrbnik
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE skrbnik (dobiva_maile BOOLEAN, otrok INTEGER REFERENCES otrok (id), stars INTEGER REFERENCES stars (id), PRIMARY KEY (otrok, stars))

objects.name: skupina
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE skupina (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, ime TEXT, stevilo_treningov INTEGER, trener INTEGER REFERENCES trener (id))

objects.name: smer
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE smer (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, ime TEXT, plezalisce INTEGER REFERENCES plezalisce (id), tezavnost TEXT)

objects.name: stars
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE stars (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, ime TEXT, priimek TEXT, mail TEXT, naslov TEXT, telefon TEXT)

objects.name: trener
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE trener (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, ime TEXT, priimek TEXT, mail TEXT, naslov TEXT, telefon TEXT)
